rows.label: qst002207_msg0001
rows.name: Um... Hello! A-are you Albina?

rows.label: qst002207_msg0002
rows.name: Mellica...?

rows.label: qst002207_msg0003
rows.name:
I never thought you'd come to me
on your own.

rows.label: qst002207_msg0004
rows.name:
I was just wondering when the best
time would be to go and take you out.

rows.label: qst002207_msg0005
rows.name: T-take me...out...?

rows.label: qst002207_msg0006
rows.name:
Y-you don't mean...
you want to...k-kill...?

rows.label: qst002207_msg0007
rows.name: Huh? I thought you knew that already.

rows.label: qst002207_msg0008
rows.name:
Isn't that why you hired these
Drivers to protect you?

rows.label: qst002207_msg0009
rows.name:
N-no! These are just some kind
people who offered to help...

rows.label: qst002207_msg0010
rows.name: I just wanted to come and talk to you!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0011
rows.name: What's to talk about?

rows.label: qst002207_msg0012
rows.name:
If it weren't for you, I would've
made it into the Choir.

rows.label: qst002207_msg0013
rows.name:
I hate you so much, you witch.
You pig. You dirty little... Urghhh!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0014
rows.name:
If it weren't for you...if I could
just get rid of you...I could have
everything I deserve!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0015
rows.name:
I could get out of this hellish life
and live like a respectable person!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0016
rows.name:
I could give my mom and dad
the rest and comfort they need!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0017
rows.name: But violence isn't going to solve any-

rows.label: qst002207_msg0018
rows.name:
Oh, but it will! And it's going to
change my life for the better!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0019
rows.name: I'm a refugee from Invidia, you know.

rows.label: qst002207_msg0020
rows.name:
I know people in the mercenary biz.
And once I kill you and join the Choir,
I'll have the cash to pay them off!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0021
rows.name:
Once I explained that, they
were glad to help.

rows.label: qst002207_msg0022
rows.name:
So I'm sorry, but I'm going to have
to make all of you disappear!

rows.label: qst002207_msg0023
rows.name: H-help! Please!
